    WADashboard: IWMI Water Accounting+ Visualization Dashboard

    Source: R/WADashboard.R
    WADashboard-package.Rd

    This package includes all dependencies to run WA+ Dashboard application either locally inside RStudio or containerized.

    Details

    R package with Shiny-based Water Accounting Plus dashboard application

    This package exposes these options:

    • wa.data: user-defined path to download remote spatio-temporal raster files
